╦George 'Uncle Boy' Clasper
01.07.1927-09.01.2009
Much loved brother and uncle who loved to walk his dogs in this park
The years in our eye we can wipe away
But the pain in our hearts will always stay"█
ž[LEFT]
Yve Ferguson
The Cromwell Hospital
August 1984 - October 2007

[CENTRE]
Yve much loved, much missed, always remembered

[RIGHT]
Yve Ferguson
